programme.title: Även anglar ater bonor
programme.desc: Fribrottaren Charlie (Bud Spencer) och drommaren Sonny (Giuliano Gemma) ar två fattiga tuffingar i 30-talets Chicago som hoppas på battre tider. De får chansen till stora pengar nar de borjar arbeta for en maffiaboss. Problemet ar att de ar alldeles for blodiga. De lånar ut pengar till fattiga istallet for att inkassera beskyddarpengar och driver hela tiden maffiabossen till vansinne. Till slut beslutar sig skurkarna for att undanroja Charlie och Sonny. Men de har glomt en sak - Charlies formidabla styrka sitter framst i navarna!

programme.title: Windtalkers
programme.desc: I det brutala slaget vid Saipan under andra varldskriget vaktar sergeant Joe Enders (Nicolas Cage) – och blir van med – Ben Yahzee (Adam Beach), en ung Navajo som ar tranad i den enda krigskod som aldrig brutits av fienden... Navajo-koden. Men om Yahzee skulle falla i fiendens hander, hur långt ar Enders beredd att gå for att radda militarens maktigaste hemlighet? John Woo regisserar detta actionfyllda epos inspirerat av den sanna historien om Navajo-soldaterna, vars mod och uppoffringar hjalpte till att vinna kriget i Stilla havet.

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: En forskare blir kidnappad och slangd ut i en dodsbringande oken dar hon måste kampa mot elementen for att overleva.

programme.title: Texas Red
programme.desc: Den sanna historien om legendariske Texas Red, en afroamerikansk man som vildsint jagades utmed prariens sargade landskap av hundratals laglosa cowboys genom Mississippis vintervildmark. Allt for att lagga beslag på den hogst eftertraktade beloningen.

programme.title: Spaghettiman
programme.desc: Clark saknar empati for allt och alla. Han skiter fullstandigt i varlden vi lever i och bryr sig knappt om sig sjalv heller. Men efter en incident med en gammal gryta fylld av spaghetti och en trasig mikro går nått fullstandigt snett. Clark forvandlas till en superhjalte som kan bekampa kriminalitet med hjalp av spaghetti. Men det finns en hake, du måste betala honom.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Det hela borjar med att en magisk spira transporterar deras goda van April genom tid och rum, anda till samurajernas Japan. Leonardo och ganget ger sig genast av efter henne, och måste nu besegra den elake Lord Naringa for att radda den insparrade April och återta spiran som lorden kommit over. Annars lar de bli fast i medeltida Japan i eviga tider. Och dar finns ju inte ens några pizzerior…

programme.title: Shockwave
programme.desc: Nar en massiv vulkanisk storm drabbar varlden forsoker geofysikern Kate Ferris overtyga forsvarsdepartementet att det inte ar ett naturligt fenomen. Det ar resultatet av ett seismiskt supervapen, kant som Hell Storm, som aktiverats. Kate måste komma på ett satt att stoppa chockvågen innan den hotar manskligheten.

programme.title: Banana Joe
programme.desc: Den italienska westernstjarnan Bud Spencer (hans riktiga namn ar Carlo Pedersoli) spelar en godhjartad men jarnnavad bananodlare som bor i en liten djungelby. Ett stort bananforetag vill exploatera byn, och nar Joe satter sig på tvaren bestammer sig foretagsledaren – en gangster – att satta dit honom. Resultatet ar ett komiskt aventyr med många energiska slagsmål.

programme.title: Man On A Ledge (2012)
programme.desc: Vågar du ta nasta steg? Den forrymde fången Nick Cassidy står plotsligt hogt upp på en avsats på en skyskrapa i New York. Kommer han att hoppa? På nolltid har Nick fångat hela stadens och alla mediers uppmarksamhet. Och medan alla tittar upp, ser ingen den utstuderade kupp som ager rum på andra sidan gatan. Hanger dessa båda handelser ihop? Kommer polispsykologen Lydia sanningen på spåren? Och har Nick i sjalva verket en helt annan agenda?

programme.title: The Fourth Musketeer
programme.desc: På uppdrag av sin far reser den unge dArtagnan från landsbygden i Gascogne till Paris, dar han blir indragen i en listig och mycket komplicerad komplott mellan kungens musketorer och kardinal Richelieus gardister. Blod ska spillas, och den som inte ar på sin vakt kommer få satta livet till.

programme.title: American Exit
programme.desc: Charlie Bond står infor ett vagskal i livet. Han har nyligen separerat från sin fru och blir ombedd att ta hand om deras son Leo over helgen. Illa tajmat då han just ar i fard med att iscensatta en konstkupp for lite snabba pengar. Leo ar helt ovetandes om planen och bara ser fram emot att får spendera tid med sin efterlangtade pappa. Tatt inpå kommer verkligheten snabbt ikapp Charlie som nu ar i allra hogsta grad en jagad man av skoningslosa torpeder. Hans enda hopp ar att lyckats fly ut ur landet och att få återstalla sin relation till Leo som han vanskott i alla år.

programme.title: Skurkar och banditer
programme.desc: Tony Roma (Tomas Milian) ar alla tiders halaste gigolo, en sol-och-vårare och skojare specialiserad på att knycka formogna hemmafruars diamanter. Till slut kopplas den hemliga polisen Parker (Bud Spencer) in for att ta fast den lille skojaren. Parker vill helst åka på semester med sin stora familj. Istallet tvingas han nu skydda Tony sedan denne blivit vittne till ett maffiamord. Sjalvklart haglar råsoparna och smockorna nar Parker tar sig an maffiaganget och kastar skurkarna rakt igenom dorrar och vaggar.

programme.title: Gun
programme.desc: Vapenrelaterat våld och en skenande brottsstatistik får polisen i Detroit att tillsammans med FBI starta ett fullskaligt krig mot stadens vapensmugglare. Rich och hans organisation blir de framsta måltavlorna for operationen. Och då Rich, hans baste van Angel, och hans alskarinna och leverantor Gabriella råkar ut for en affarsuppgorelse som går fel, avslojas en stor hemlighet som skakar Rich anda in i margen. Det blir hogexplosiv action med bland annat Val Kilmer, Curtis ”50 Cent” Jackson och Danny Trejo!

programme.title: Supersnutarna
programme.desc: De alskar fighter och planerar ett stort rån - och de ar filmnes hjaltar!Det har bara gått fem minuter av denna actionkomedi då Terence Hill och Bud Spencer redan forstort tre amerikanska vrålåk och spoat upp deras agare. Matt Kirby (Hill) och Wilbur Walsh (Spencer) ar två hårdslående bråkmakare, men med hjartat på ratta stallet. Efter ett misslyckat rånforsok i Miami hamnar de av misstag på stadens polisskola. Trots att de har svårt att skilja på ratt och fel klarar de utbildningen och utses till motorcykelpoliser. De gor sitt basta for att bli utsparkade ur poliskåren, men hur hårt de an anstranger sig går de ur varje fight som hjaltar!

programme.title: Snedseglarna
programme.desc: Alan (Terence Hill) ar en obotlig gambler som en dag spelar bort maffians pengar och måste fly for livet. Han hinner dock få med sig sin farbrors hemliga skattkarta och gommer sig på jordenruntseglaren Charlies (Bud Spencer) båt. Alan trixar med kompassen och snart når det udda paret den paradisiska soderhavso dar skatten ar nedgravd.Har finns emellertid också fientliga infodingar, manniskojagare och en japan som fortfarande tror att andra varldskriget pågår for fullt. Alan och Charlie slåss mot dem alla och har de ingen annan att fightas mot — ger de sig på varandra! Det farsartade aventyret ”Snedseglarna” visas nu for forsta gången i oklippt originalversion.

programme.title: Legacy of lies
programme.desc: Scott Adkins spelar den hårde dorrvakten Martin Baxter som drygar ut inkomsterna genom att stalla upp i måttligt lagliga kampsportstavlingar. I bakgrunden finns en karriar som MI6-agent han lamnade efter ett uppdrag i Kiev som slutade med katastrof. Men det forflutna har ju en tendens att hinna ikapp folk inom hans profession. Nar Baxter får chansen att grava fram vad det egentligen var som hande den dar odesdigra kvallen i Kiev tar han den.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Raining in the Mountain
programme.desc: I ett buddhisttempel i Mingdynastins Kina ar det dags for abboten att utse sin eftertradare. Men bland kandidaterna finns det de som framst ar ute efter att stjala den ovarderliga skriften i templets skattkammare. Intriger och allianser uppstår nar personliga ambitioner och andliga stravanden kolliderar.

programme.title: Legal Action
programme.desc: Stjarnadvokaten Casey McKay lockas till en liten stad av sin exfru for att forsvara hennes bror som står åtalad for att ha mordat en distriktsåklagare. Casey blottlagger en konspirationsharva som staller honom oga mot oga med mr Gates, stadens allra mest korrupte markexploator. En f.d. marinsoldat hjalper Casey i konflikten nar det står klart att han behover mer an sitt juridiska kunnande for att hålla sig vid liv och radda sin klient.

programme.title: Fungi
programme.desc: En svamporganism har slagit ut storre delen av jordens befolkning. I en bunker någonstans i Sverige har ett forskarteam isolerat sig och kampar for att hitta ett botemedel. 19-åriga Leah forsoker anpassa sig till denna instangda tillvaro med sin pappa, militaren Gustav. Forskarduon Vera och Kim ser hoppet om en battre framtid hotas nar bunkerns ventilationssystem går sonder. Teamet tvingas ut på en farlig resa och det visar sig snart att svamporganismen inte ar det enda livsfarliga hotet i varlden utanfor.

programme.title: Impact Earth
programme.desc: En astronomiprofessor som jobbat for NASA inser att en destruktiv asteroid ar på kollisionskurs med jorden och måste få sin familj i sakerhet samtidigt som han varnar varlden for denna hotande forodelse.

programme.title: TMNT
programme.desc: Splittra; råttan sensei; kanner att hans fyra tonåriga skoldpaddslarjungar har vuxit isar och behover knyta an for att besegra ett uråldrigt monster.

programme.title: Triassic Hunt
programme.desc: Nar två genetiskt framtagna dinousarer rymmer från laboratoriet kallas en styrka legosoldater in for att fånga dem. Men nar soldaterna inser att dinousarerna ar lika smarta som manniskor borjar en katt och råttalek utan dess like.

programme.title: USS Indianapolis: Men of Courage
programme.desc: I slutet av andra varldskriget fraktade den amerikanska tunga kryssaren USS Indianapolis i hemlighet en av de två atombomber som skulle komma att avsluta kriget. En japansk ubåt anfoll och sankte fartyget. USS Indianapolis uppdrag var så hemligt att fartyget inte anmaldes saknat och ingen visste att fartyget hade sankts forran forst fyra dagar senare. Av de 1197 ombord foljde nastan 300 med sitt fartyg i djupet. De overlevande blev liggande i de hajrika vattnen i Filippinska sjon och tvingades att utstå hunger, torst, hetta, hallucinationer, ideliga hajangrepp och många av sina skeppskamraters dod. Fem dagar senare levde bara 317 man och dessa kunde till slut raddas.

programme.title: Blue Steel
programme.desc: For en nyexaminerad polis finns det en sak som ar farligare an att visa upp en mordares fantasi. Att bli den.

programme.title: Skumma polare
programme.desc: Trinityseriens stjarna Bud Spencer återvander till vilda vastern i regissoren Michele Lupo’s komedi om bedragaren Buddy, som misstas for en lakare efter att hans van Cocoa oavsiktligt stjal en resvaska med kirurgiska instrument. Buddy bosatter sig i den lilla staden som en experimentell lakare. Nar ett gang våldsamma brottslingar forsoker ta over staden, visar det sig att hans sanna talang ar att slå ner skurkar synkad till musik som humoristiskt komponerats av spaghettivastmastaren Ennio Morricone.

programme.title: Street Fighter: The Legend Of Chun-Li
programme.desc: Efter det att hennes pappa blivit kidnappad tar Chun-Li steget ner i Hong Kongs brutala undre varld - torstande efter hamnd och på vag mot den ultimata konfrontationen med den storsta fiende hon någonsin kommer att mota. De stålhårda smockorna hanger i luften nar Street Fighter ar tillbaka!

programme.title: The U.S. East Coast
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 The U.S. East Coast, The Southern States
programme.desc: We travel from Georgia through the Carolinas to Virginia, ending near Washington, DC. Along the way we meet a Georgia farmer; talk to painter J. Chris Wilson in Charleston; sail along the Outer Banks of Carolina, and visit rural Virginia, experiencing life in the beautiful southern states.

programme.title: Hummingbirds: Jewelled Messengers
programme.desc: Hummingbirds live at the limits of what is possible. They have the highest metabolism with a heart rate of 1,200 beats per minute of any vertebrate. Their wings beat 50 times a second. They can hover on the spot, and even fly backwards. To our eyes, they are just a blur. But with the aid of high-speed cameras we can slow down their hyperactive lives and look into their secret world.

programme.title: Snowy Owl: Queen of the North
programme.desc: No other owls are capable of surviving the extreme conditions, whereas the snowy owl is able to hunt through six months of bright sunshine and six months of twilight. This film follows a pair of snowy owls as they breed on the tundra of the High Arctic, 300 miles inside the Arctic Circle. Lemming numbers are low this year. Five owlets hatch and they face a struggle if any are going to survive.

programme.title: The Secret of Migrating Birds - Tryst at the Red Sea
programme.desc: Each year in spring, Israel witnesses a unique spectacle. Many millions of migrating birds cross the land bridge between Africa, Asia and Europe.Their first major roosting place after an exhausting nonstop flight over the African deserts is in southern Israel – a vital stopover. Here they replenish their energy reserves. The flocks of migrating birds are pursued by flocks of ornithologists. Hundreds of birders flood into the port city of Eilat on the Red Sea to take part in the Migration Festival. For a week, Israels southernmost coastal resort is home to international scientists and amateur birders.

programme.title: Penguin City - South Georgia
programme.desc: In the middle of the Antarctic Ocean, an entire mountain range arises from the water: South Georgia, the nursery of the Antarctic. Hundreds of thousands of penguins, elephant seals, fur seals and their young overcrowd the beaches. The rough weather and the extremely difficult access to the island cause filmmaking to be an endeavor requiring much of the film crew around Roland Gockel and Rosie Koch and the state of the art cameras. A lot of patience and sensitivity over a period spanning some five years now offers unknown and poignant insights into the life of the King Penguins on South Georgia Island

programme.title: Cuckoo - The Enemy in My Nest
programme.desc: It’s no news that cuckoos are brood parasites: they lay their eggs into the nests of other bird species – a clever trick that spares the rearing of own offspring. Some even go as far as to kill the other chicks in the nest. But why do other parent birds let this happen? Are they too stupid? Too inept? Or simply clueless? Admittedly, cuckoo’s eggs do look deceptively genuine. But the cuckoo chick? Not even remotely! It quickly grows into a giant that looks nothing like its new family. Turns out: they may even profit from having strangers’...

programme.title: King of the Mountains - Golden Eagle
programme.desc: Aerial shots of mating Golden eagles, a clash between a Golden and a White-tailed eagle, and an intimate glimpse into their nesting grounds combine to create a spectacular film. Tracking these majestic birds reveals the wild nature of their hunting grounds, showcasing the diverse animal and plant life that share their habitat with the king of the skies. Viewers are brought up close as the eagle effortlessly glides over forests and canyons, abruptly diving in a breathtaking pursuit of prey. Witnessing these birds in their natural habitats is witnessing them at their finest. Embark on a magnificent journey through the skies and landscapes with us.

programme.title: Hunters of the Skies
programme.desc: Birds of prey are symbols of power, speed and splendour. In fact, there are very few species in the animal kingdom that can be described in as many superlatives. Their amazing use of different senses, their incredible feats of flight as well as their multitude of different hunting strategies are simply astounding. Hawks, buzzards and eagles have conquered every habitat on earth - from the dry arid south, to the cool and moist river valleys, to the coasts of Norway, all the way up to the sparse high mountains. Some of them, like the incredibly versatile hawk, can even hunt in the forest. Their literal eagle eye vision is unrivaled in the animal kingdom. All birds of prey sustain themselves...

programme.title: Down to Earth - Flightless Birds
programme.desc: They’ve given up the wonderful art of flying. Or was it an art they never possessed? The brain structure and anatomy of flightless birds indicate that they descended from "flyers" – so, why don’t they fly?

programme.title: Germanys Wild Birds
programme.desc: By monitoring ten interesting bird-watching locations, we document not only the silver herons in the Westerwald, but also the last great bustards in Havelland. Then there are the great crested grebes in their splendid plumages, shown building their nests and during courtship, in an area of extinct volcanoes: the Eiffel. Add to this, exotic wild birds and colorful parakeets, the newest members of the population in a park in Wiesbaden. We have resting migratory birds, ducks and waders on the west banks of the Steinhuder Lake. On the border to the Netherlands, in the moorlands near Munster, we find the only wild flamingos in Germany. Equally interesting are the fire geese, avocets and many...

programme.title: King of the Seas - Sea Eagle
programme.desc: The times where eagles have been seen as varmints are over. They are now perceived as an integral part of the food cycle. Due to the fact that the habitats of the sea eagles in Germany are largely found in the north-eastern regions that are rich in water, the movie accompanies the eagles to an island, home to hundreds of sea ravens, where they rob the baby sea ravens of their food. They seem to always profit from the successes of the fellow creatures in their habitats. This film introduces you to the expert poachers of the animal kingdom.

programme.title: Eagles - Masters Of The Skies
programme.desc: Whether in Alaska or in the Dolomites, eagles are generally seen as Kings of the skies. This film devotes itself on the one hand to the bald eagle, the heraldic bird of the United States, and on the other, the Golden Eagle, Europes largest predatory bird. Many bald eagles live in the Chilkoot State Park in Alaskas south. In fact, more than 400 pairs reside there for the entire year. With a wingspan of some 2.5 metres, they are amongst the largest of their species. The offspring have to leave the eyrie by September at the latest, as then, winter sets in. On clear, starry nights, one can experience the Northern Lights. There are certain places where especially many eagles group. 3000 to...

programme.title: A Winters Tale - The Journey of the Snowy Owls
programme.desc: Snowy owls live a life full of mystery up in the Arctic. Thousands of years ago, they built a community of fate with their neighbors – lemmings. About every four years, lemmings proliferate in huge numbers. This way, snowy owls have enough feed for their young. The owls lay up to eleven eggs and can successfully raise the chicks – each of them needs two to four lemmings per day. Lately, however, lemmings’ mass reproduction hasn’t been as regular in some parts of the Tundra. What will happen to them and the snowy owls? What is the ecological link here? And what will happen if one year the winter arrives way too early? The best way for many birds to adapt to the winter is to flee to the...

programme.title: Beak and Brain - Genius Birds from Down Under
programme.desc: These child prodigies of the animal kingdom have feathers and beaks – and very special skills! The Keas of New Zealand are the only parrots that live in snowy mountain areas. They like testing their brains, solving puzzles and challenging tourists: they unscrew bottle-tops, dismantle windscreen wiper blades and tear open rucksacks. They seem so determined you’d think they have an understanding of physics and mechanics! Thousands of miles northwards, in New Caledonia, other birds have talent, too. Here bird expert Gavin Hunt discovered that crows are able to produce a whole set of tools, each designed for a particular purpose – the most intricate tool culture in the animal kingdom! These...

programme.title: Children of the Sun
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Children of the Sun - Butterflies
programme.desc: Butterflies surely are the most fancied species inside the insect world. Their beautiful colouring and their graceful flight appeal to everyone. There are close to 4000 types of Butterflies – today many of them are endangered due to the loss of their habitat.

programme.title: Children of the Sun
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Children of the Sun - Wild Bees
programme.desc: Most people associate honey producing insects with the name “BEE“. Few realize that there are over 560 different species of bees - most of them live their lives “busy as a bee“ but some “abuse“ other insects and others are even known to be murderers. The film “Wild Bees” shows the incredible diversity and the stunning adaptations of our “BEES” to various habitats and diverse living conditions. Fascinating fights, sensational performances, imposing structures and colorful individuals – the world of “Wild Bees” offers all of this and more.

programme.title: Hummingbirds: Jewelled Messengers
programme.desc: Hummingbirds live at the limits of what is possible. They have the highest metabolism with a heart rate of 1,200 beats per minute of any vertebrate. Their wings beat 50 times a second. They can hover on the spot, and even fly backwards. To our eyes, they are just a blur. But with the aid of high-speed cameras we can slow down their hyperactive lives and look into their secret world.

programme.title: Snowy Owl: Queen of the North
programme.desc: No other owls are capable of surviving the extreme conditions, whereas the snowy owl is able to hunt through six months of bright sunshine and six months of twilight. This film follows a pair of snowy owls as they breed on the tundra of the High Arctic, 300 miles inside the Arctic Circle. Lemming numbers are low this year. Five owlets hatch and they face a struggle if any are going to survive.

programme.title: The Secret of Migrating Birds - Tryst at the Red Sea
programme.desc: Each year in spring, Israel witnesses a unique spectacle. Many millions of migrating birds cross the land bridge between Africa, Asia and Europe.Their first major roosting place after an exhausting nonstop flight over the African deserts is in southern Israel – a vital stopover. Here they replenish their energy reserves. The flocks of migrating birds are pursued by flocks of ornithologists. Hundreds of birders flood into the port city of Eilat on the Red Sea to take part in the Migration Festival. For a week, Israels southernmost coastal resort is home to international scientists and amateur birders.

programme.title: Penguin City - South Georgia
programme.desc: In the middle of the Antarctic Ocean, an entire mountain range arises from the water: South Georgia, the nursery of the Antarctic. Hundreds of thousands of penguins, elephant seals, fur seals and their young overcrowd the beaches. The rough weather and the extremely difficult access to the island cause filmmaking to be an endeavor requiring much of the film crew around Roland Gockel and Rosie Koch and the state of the art cameras. A lot of patience and sensitivity over a period spanning some five years now offers unknown and poignant insights into the life of the King Penguins on South Georgia Island

programme.title: Cuckoo - The Enemy in My Nest
programme.desc: It’s no news that cuckoos are brood parasites: they lay their eggs into the nests of other bird species – a clever trick that spares the rearing of own offspring. Some even go as far as to kill the other chicks in the nest. But why do other parent birds let this happen? Are they too stupid? Too inept? Or simply clueless? programme.desc: Tenerife is outstanding among the Canary Islands. If only because of the volcano Pico del Teide, which rises exactly 3.718 meters above sea level and is thus the highest mountain in Spain. But not only scenically Tenerife, the largest of the Canary Islands, stands out...

programme.title: Fuerteventura: The golden beauty of the Canaries
programme.desc: Fuerteventura, the second largest of the Canary Islands, is located just 120 kilometres off the coast of West Africa. The climate is extremely dry and the struggle for water has always been a major setback. Then, around a century ago, returning US emigrants brought what were then modern wind turbine water pumps from the Aermotor Windmill Company with them to Fuerte-ventura. Today, the environmentally friendly and so-called “Chicago’s”, experience a renaissance. Unfortu-nately, original spare parts in good condition are diffi-cult to come by. programme.title: Dream Islands of Europe: Lanzarote and Fuerteventura
programme.desc: The film presents the two Canary Islands Lanzarote and Fuerteventura. Lanzarote has a rich culture in addition to a volcanic landscape: the film accompanies a ceramic artist, an instrument maker, shows architecture by Cesar Manrique and a camel breeder. On Fuerteventura, in addition to livestock farming and the operation of traditional grain mills, nature conservation plays a major role: islanders are committed to preserving the sand dunes, and there is a turtle hatchery. On Lanzarote, countless volcanic eruptions have formed a bizarre lunar landscape. It is a great challenge for the inhabitants to extract the cultivation of food from the karstic, dry soil. And yet they even manage to...

programme.title: The Provence coast - Marseille and the Côte Bleue
programme.desc: The Provence is famed for its endless fields of laven-der, but this lush landscape also has a beautifully mari-time touch: The Côte Bleue! Small, hidden beaches, charming harbour towns, imposing, craggy bays and a uniquely clear light that has attracted painters includ-ing Cezanne and Braque. The coast derives its name from the deep blue water and extends from Marseille to Martigues. This small town is also known as "The Ven-ice of the North", as it is shaped entirely by water: an inland lake, the sea itself, as well as a connecting canal. In the bays of the Calanques, the steeply-walled coastal inlets in the Mediterranean limestone, Lionel Franc is a cliff diver. His personal record is a...

programme.title: Europe`s Forgotten Pilgrim Routes
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Europe`s Forgotten Pilgrim Routes: England: The Pilgrims Way to Canterbury
programme.desc: In the Middle Ages, the horrifying murder of Archbishop Thomas Becket of Canterbury led thousands of pilgrims to the south of England. Centuries later, the long-forgotten Pilgrims Way is now enjoying a revival. The Pilgrims Way leads east to west cross-country from Winchester to Canterbury through the counties of Hampshire, Surrey and Kent.

programme.title: Europe`s Forgotten Pilgrim Routes
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Europe`s Forgotten Pilgrim Routes: France: The Mont-Saint-Michel Way
programme.desc: In honour of the Archangel Michael, thousands of medieval Christians set off on pilgrimages to the famous mountain monastery of the Mont-Saint-Michel in the Atlantic Ocean. Today it continues to enchant millions of visitors each year. But the pilgrimage route from Rouen to the mountain abbey seems to have been forgotten: it leads through the depths of Normandy into rural France.

programme.title: Europe`s Forgotten Pilgrim Routes
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Europe`s Forgotten Pilgrim Routes: Switzerland, Italy: The VIA FRANCIGENA to Rome
programme.desc: For centuries, pilgrims have set off on the Via Francigena in the hopes of reaching the tombs of the apostles Peter and Paul in Rome. The ancient pilgrimage route leads through the imposing Alps to the Great St Bernard Pass and from there cross-country through Italy.

programme.title: mareTV: Venice - Lagoon and Legend
programme.desc: Venice has been attracting people as if by magic for centuries. The Italians call her La Serenissima, or the sublime. Perched on wooden posts, she braves the elements and the huge, annual surge of visitors. Vogalonga is the name of a Venetian sports competition for women, in which the participants row their boats standing. This is a tradition that Guilia and Elena also follow. They train hard, as the yearly regatta is soon to begin. Anyone caught driving their water vehicle with more than 7 km/h through the canals of Venice, risks getting a ticket from local policewoman Lorenza Mariutti. The reason: the resulting waves gnaw at the foundations of the grand palaces. Venetians are very...

programme.title: mareTV: Majorca
programme.desc: "Cleaning woman island", concrete castles, Ballermann: Mallorcas image is negatively affected in some respects. The documentary explores the charm of the largest Balearic island beyond the hustle and bustle of tourism and Rambazamba. The "real" Mallorca is best explored through real Majorcans: Manolo Barahona, TV fishing expert from the local island broadcaster IB3, faces the most difficult task of the year. The Raor is in season, the most expensive fish on the island. Manolo is supposed to get him first in front of the camera and then in the pan. Theres only one catch, the little fish with the piranha teeth just doesnt want to be on TV. In the first months of the year Mallorca turns...

programme.title: Menorca - Majorcas beautiful sister
programme.desc: Not nearly as crowded as Majorca or Ibiza: Menorca has noticeably fewer visitors than her sister islands and in 1993, was recognised by UNESCO as a biosphere re-serve. Menorca also has its own distinctive charm, with its secluded coves, mighty cliffs, beautiful gardens and ages old towns and villages. Its residents love the is-lands treasures and peculiarities. Forests make up al-most a third of Menorca, complemented by many lush green meadows. Next to tourism, agriculture is a major source of the islands income to the present day. On Menorca, there are several accumulations of enormous megalithic stones. From a global point of view, the up to five-metre-tall "Taulas", whereby the stones...

programme.title: mareTV: La Palma: The Greenest of the Canaries
programme.desc: Thundering waterfalls, ancient forests and an impressive volcanic landscape with black beaches: La Palma is a dream island for nature lovers. It is by far the island of the Canary Islands with the most green, almost half of it is covered with forest. But once a year the green island is dominated by the color white. On Rosenmontag (Rose Monday), the inhabitants have for decades been targeting those ancestors who returned from abroad wealthy and ostentatiously demonstrated their wealth with powdered faces. The carnivalistic approach culminates every year in a white chaos, with tons of talcum, flour or paint trickling down the uniformly white dressed islanders. On the Roque de los Muchachos,...

programme.title: mareTV: Ibiza - Island of Light
programme.desc: The light of the Balearic island of Ibiza is magical and its trademark: The "Island of Light" is tiny compared to its sister island Mallorca, but offers the most beautiful sunsets in the world. Thats what they say. They attract sun worshippers and party people from near and far. To the sounds of the famous "Balearic Sound" they turn night into day. This documentary documents the island in the balancing act between luxury yachts and traditions. Hippie culture, celebrities, pine forests, bays with turquoise water and villages with bright white houses: Ibiza has many faces. Mora (80) and Djin (67) have been drawn to the island for 55 years. They are the uncrowned kings of the hippies. But...

programme.title: mareTV: The white wilderness in Greenlands East
programme.desc: Fjords, glaciers and the highest mountains in the Arctic: East Greenland with its spectacular nature is one of the most sparsely populated regions on earth. The people here live in extreme isolation and depend on helicopter flights for their supplies. Despite harsh conditions, the inhabitants here lovingly maintain their traditions and enjoy their outdoor leisure time even at minus 20 degrees Celsius. The town of Tasiilaq is the "metropolis" with 4,000 inhabitants and offers a very special attraction: the only ski lift on the east coast. Thomas Mikaelsen, the lift attendant, is not to be envied for his job. The only 100 meter long lift comes from Switzerland and is already 20 years old....

programme.title: The Cape of Wild Animals, Episode 5
programme.desc: The movie focuses on committed animal rights activists, who fight for the lives of their charges every day, in diverse protection projects and rescue centres along the South African Garden Route.

programme.title: Lions On The Move
programme.desc: Kevin Richardson shares an extraordinary bond with Africa’s most fearsome predators. Together with them, he has experienced some real adventures. However, transporting 27 lions and 14 hyenas to a new home presents a different challenge.The lions new home will be a sanctuary on the edge of Dinokeng, a South African game reserve spanning 18,000 square metres. The huge task ahead includes planning and designing the new enclosures, and securing permits to move the animals.

programme.title: Lions On The Move
programme.desc: Not only are the animals regularly rotated into new enclosures to prevent repetitive behaviour developing out of boredom, but Kevin also has to practice loading them in and out of the van. Can the reluctant lions and hyenas eventually be persuaded to get on board with the move?

programme.title: I Got a Monster: Americas Most Corrupt Police Squad
programme.desc: Retells in highly dramatic fashion one of the USAs biggest police corruption scandals. In 2017, Baltimore was rocked by the Federal indictment of Wayne Jenkins, a highly decorated supercop and leader of the Baltimore Police Departments elite Gun Trace Task Force along with six other members on racketeering charges.

programme.title: OJ25

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Reality?
programme.desc: Part 1 of this 5-part series of shorts introduces the world of the visual scientist. Beyond boggling your mind, Prof. Arthur Shapiro explains how you see what you see.

programme.title: Brightness And Contrast
programme.desc: In part 2 of this series of shorts, Prof. Arthur Shapiro takes us through visual illusions that show how our brain processes retinal impressions from light and dark.

programme.title: Motion
programme.desc: In part 3 of the five-part series, Prof. Shapiro shows us that the brain is challenged to process some stimuli from the eyes and sometimes "guesses" what you are seeing.

programme.title: The Classics
programme.desc: In this 4th installment of the series, Prof. Arthur Shapiro returns to the classic visual illusions that show us that what we see is not exactly in plain sight.

programme.title: Grouping
programme.desc: In the final short program of the series, Prof. Shapiro offers us more challenging questions about the way we see as he shows us how light that hits the retina is interpreted by the brain.

programme.title: Ambiguous Images
programme.desc: Professor Shapiro shows us how some images can prompt two, or even three, equally valid interpretations - leading to some baffling and astonishing visual experiences.

programme.title: Impossible Objects
programme.desc: Professor Shapiro shows us a range of objects that seem simple and unremarkable at first glance, but which on closer examination simply cannot be constructed in reality.

programme.title: Perspective Games
programme.desc: Professor Shapiro reaches back into history to show that artists, architects and mathematicians have also employed visual “tricks” to baffle and entertain us.

programme.title: Reversing Alzheimers
programme.desc: As the number of people affected by Alzheimers Disease continues to grow at an unprecedented pace, researchers worldwide are racing to discover a cure.

programme.title: Fixing A Broken Heart
programme.desc: Heart disease is the number one cause of deaths worldwide, but there are researchers frantically working to change that. Meet the people inventing the future of cardia...

programme.title: Making Babies
programme.desc: How close are we to rendering infertility a problem of the past?

programme.title: Hacking our Microbiome
programme.desc: Every person is playing host to at least 40 trillion non-human microorganisms. Collectively, these microbes constitute whats called our microbiome.

programme.title: Raising A Genius
programme.desc: Every child has a gift, and all of us as human beings have a contribution that we can make to society, and we just have to find what that is. But what does it take to create a genius? What should the education of a genius look like?

programme.title: Can You Learn to Be Funny?
programme.desc: What do you get when you cross a clown teacher, a comedian and neuroscientist? Surprising new insights about what it takes to be funny.

programme.title: The Science of Cute
programme.desc: Domestication shaped wolves into dogs and transformed both their behavior and their anatomy. New discoveries show how dogs produce a very specific eyebrow movement more often than wolves do. But how and why did “puppy dog eyes” develop in domesticated dogs?

programme.title: Top Science Stories of 2020
programme.desc: 2020 has been an unprecedented year in science. From a global pandemic and race to find a cure, to exploring our planetary neighbors and our own world.

programme.title: Incendies
programme.desc: Nar notarien Lebel (Remy Girard) ska lasa upp Nawals testamente for hennes barn Jeanne och Simon, upptacker de två kuvert: ett till den far de trodde var dod, och ett till en bror som de inte visste om. Detta ar borjan på en upptacktsresa i deras doda mors fotspår, och Jeanne och Simon kan borja pussla ihop historien om kvinnan som fott och fostrat dem. Det blir en berattelse om hat, krig och enastående mod. Och till slut återstår bara en pusselbit: att hitta deras okande bror. Den enda ledtråden ar den speciella tatuering av tre svarta prickar som han har på foten. Kanadas Oscarsbidrag 2011.

programme.title: In Tranzit
programme.desc: Baserad på en sann historia. I chockvågorna efter andra varldskriget, under den kalla vintern 1946, skickas av misstag en grupp tyska krigsfångar till ett ryskt kvinnofånglager som styrs av kvinnliga fångvaktare. Fångvaktarna, som forlorat många narstående på grund av Nazisternas brutalitet, mottar de nyanlanda fångarna med stor fientlighet och ser en mojlighet till hamnd...

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Varg
programme.desc: Varg ar en storslagen film om Klemens (Peter Stormare) och hans systerson Nejla som lever mitt i det norrlandska landskapet på gransen mellan Sverige och Norge.

programme.title: Mothers and Daughters
programme.desc: Från ett hoghus på Manhattan kikar den hippa och lyckliga singeltjejen Rigby Gray in i sina grannars lagenheter och liv. Hon kanner sig trygg bakom sitt långa kameraobjektiv och ar helt omedveten om att hennes liv snart kommer att forandras for all framtid. Rigbys ogonblicksbilder ur manniskors vardag får liv i de sammanlankade historierna om olika relationer mellan mammor och deras barn av alla de slag och i alla brokiga former. Vi ser hur syster och framling, rumskompis och karlekspartner och till och med en mardromssvarmor kan vara otroligt karleksfulla modersfigurer.

programme.title: Miss Potter
programme.desc: Hon har fascinerat generationer av lasare, men hennes liv var en hemlighet. Fram tills nu Beatrix Potter ar en ogift 30-årig kvinna i en tid då kvinnans framsta uppgift ar att gifta sig fornamt och veta sin plats. Ingen, och framforallt inte Beatrix familj, kan forstå att hon hellre vill rita och forfatta små berattelser om djur. Och helt tokigt går det nar hon moter den oerfarne forlaggaren Norman Wayne. Han foralskar sig hals over huvud i både Beatrix och i hennes unika sagor. Och han staller Beatrix infor ett omojligt uppdrag - hon måste frigora sig från sin kravande familj.

programme.title: The Good Heart
programme.desc: Jaques (Brian Cox – THE BOURNE IDENTITY) ager en sjaskig bar, som fungerar som ett andra hem for en brokig skara professionella drinkare. Jaques sjalv ar fast besluten att supa och roka sig till dods. Nar han moter den unge hemlose Lucas (Paul Dano – THERE WILL BE BLOOD), som också gett upp hoppet om livet, tycker han sig ha hittat den perfekte arvingen till baren. Jaques borjar lara Lucas sitt kungadomes manschauvernistiska lagar: inga nya kunder, ingen personlig kontakt med gasterna, och absolut inga kvinnor! Lucas lar sig fort, men vanskapen satts på prov då den olyckliga och vackra April (Isild Le Besco) soker skydd i baren.

programme.title: Sommarminnen
programme.desc: Helène ar familjens matriark, och har agnat sitt liv åt att samla konst och antikviteter. Nar hennes liv till slut kommer till anda står hennes tre barn med ett stort arv i form av ett vackert gammalt lantgods och allt det huserar, men de ar allt annat an overens om hur dessa slaktklenoder ska forvaltas. Sommarminnen ar Guldpalmsvinnaren Olivier Assayas starka familjedrama med Juliette Binoche, Charles Berling och Jeremie Renier.

programme.title: Evil Stepmom
programme.desc: Ett tvillingpar vill hjalpa sin pappa att borja dejta igen och skapar en profil på en dejtingsajt åt honom. Det drojer inte lange forran han får svar. En av tvillingflickorna blir van med pappans dejts dotter. Snart inser hon att det ar något som inte stammer. Men hur ska hon få sin nyforalskade pappa att inse allvaret?

programme.title: The Truth Commissioner
programme.desc: En sanningskommissionar avslojar morka hemligheter i Nordirland, dar makt och forflutet kolliderar i kampen for rattvisa och forsoning.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: Fast Girls
programme.desc: Nar kaxiga och gatsmarta Shania (Lenora Crichlow) traffar den ambitiosa medelklasstjejen Lisa (Lily James) kolliderar deras två varldar på loparbanan med explosiva foljder. De två sprintertjejerna kampar for att kvala in till VM i friidrott och moter tuffa motgångar och bitter rivalitet på sin dramatiska, hjartevarmande och inspirerande resa.

programme.title: The Architect
programme.desc: En arkitekt hamnar i konflikt med en aktivist som bor i ett farligt komplex som arkitekten ritade.

programme.title: Candy
programme.desc: Heath Ledger ar den hoppfulla poeten Dan som hals over huvud foralskar sig i konstnaren Candy (Abbie Cornish). Dan ar heroinmissbrukare, men Candy ar fascinerad och dras till honom. Tillsammans beger de sig ut på ostadig mark, sammanbundna av deras vansinniga karlek och glupska sexuella aptit. Med hjalp av universitetsprofessorn Casper (Geoffrey Rush), som kan skaffa dem pengar och få gratis droger, inleder de båda bohemerna en farlig flort med doden.

programme.title: Palo Alto
programme.desc: High School-eleverna Teddy, April, Fred och Emily ar som alla andra på jakt efter något att gora i Palo Altos tråkiga forortsmiljo. April ar vilsen och dras mellan en attraktion till sin aldre fotbollstranare och en oskuldsfull foralskelse i Teddy – en strulig skejtare vars kompis Fred bojar tappa greppet. Den lika vilsna Emily anvander istallet sex for att få bekraftelse.

programme.title: Journeyman
programme.desc: Efter att ha vunnit en tuff titelmatch på poang, kollapsar mellanviktsmastaren Matty Burton. Resan for att få tillbaka minnet och formågan att tala och rora sig blir hans tuffaste match någonsin och priset kan bli skyhogt då relationen till frun Emma och dottern Mia står på spel.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.
En ung forfattare tvingas att acceptera sin dodlighet nar han diagnoseras med en sallsynt form av cancer. Med hjalp av sin basta van och en ung terapeut finner han modet att mota sjukdomen.

programme.title: The Dark Divide
programme.desc: En dramakomedi som baserar sig på verkliga handelser, med David Cross - som vi sett i serien Arrested Development, och Debra Messing - kand från serien Will and Grace, i huvudrollerna. Robert ar en fjarilsforskare vars fru insjuknar i cancer. Frun overtalar sin uppgivne man att åka på en fjarilsresa, vars ovantade moten och forvantade motgångar oppnar Roberts ogon på nytt.

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Dinner Rush
programme.desc: Dinner Rush utspelar sig under vad som från borjan inte tycks vara något annat an en helt vanlig jaktig kvall på Louis Cropas (Danny Aiello) populara restaurang Gigino i det fashionabla TriBeCa-kvarteret i New York. En gång var trattorian en enkel familjerestaurang men nu har den forvandlats till kvarterets mesta innekrog, stallet dar alla vill bli sedda. Detta mycket tack vare krogaren Cropas son Udos (Edoardo Ballerini) innovativa matlagningskonst som kommit att bli stallets kannetecken. Och just den har kvallen ar restaurangen som ett kalejdoskop av livet i dagens New York...

programme.title: Son of the South
programme.desc: Verklig historia om en KKK-medlems barnbarn som vaxer upp i borjan av 1960-talet. Trots att han fostrats in i hatet intresserar han sig for medborgarrattsrorelsen.

programme.title: Bekas
programme.desc: Tidigt 90-tal, Saddam Husseins regim har satt stor press på den kurdiska delen av Irak. Två hemlosa kurdiska pojkar ser Superman på stadens forsta biograf och bestammer sig for att ta sig till Amerika. For att komma dit behover de pass, pengar och en hel del tur. Tyvarr har de inget av detta men de borjar andå resan som ska ta dem mot drommen om Amerika.

programme.title: Mazes and Monsters
programme.desc: Robbie och hans collegekompisar ar alla besatta av rollspelet "Mazes and Monsters". Men spelen tar en marklig vandning nar Robbie borjar få visioner efter att de spelat en session på ett mystiskt, lokalt landmarke.

programme.title: Auggie
programme.desc: Felix Greystone har en bit kvar till pensionsåldern, men foretaget pressar honom att gå i fortidspension. I avskedsgåva får han ett par smartglasogon, som vacker anvandarens storsta drommar till liv. Nar Felix frus karriar tar fart och dottern borjar bli sjalvstandig inser Felix hur ensam han kanner sig. For att fly den plågsamma ensamheten fordjupar Felix sig allt mer i sina smartglasogons varld, vilket påfrestar Felix relation till familjen ytterligare.

programme.title: Brain On Fire
programme.desc: Susannah Cahalan har nyligen avslutat sina universitetsstudier och lever dromlivet i New York. Hon ar en lovande journalist på New York Post och foralskad i musikern Stephen. Hennes chef ger henne det stora uppdraget som ska rivstarta hennes karriar och livet kan inte bli battre. Snart borjar saker och ting gå fel. Susannah drabbas av en influensa som inte vill ge sig, hon glommer saker och missar deadlines på jobbet. Hon hor att folk pratar om henne, ar overtygad om att Stephen har en annan flickvan och hon kan inte kontrollera sin kropp. Det blir snart varre; Susannah borjar få våldsamma anfall och hennes alltmer psykotiska upptradande innebar att hon standigt måste overvakas.

programme.title: Incendies
programme.desc: Nar notarien Lebel (Remy Girard) ska lasa upp Nawals testamente for hennes barn Jeanne och Simon, upptacker de två kuvert: ett till den far de trodde var dod, och ett till en bror som de inte visste om. Detta ar borjan på en upptacktsresa i deras doda mors fotspår, och Jeanne och Simon kan borja pussla ihop historien om kvinnan som fott och fostrat dem. Det blir en berattelse om hat, krig och enastående mod. Och till slut återstår bara en pusselbit: att hitta deras okande bror. Den enda ledtråden ar den speciella tatuering av tre svarta prickar som han har på foten. Kanadas Oscarsbidrag 2011.

programme.title: Just Before I Go
programme.desc: Courteney Cox långfilmsdebuterar som regissor med en lika hjartevarm som kolsvart komedi om enstoringen Ted Morgan. Ted vill inget annat an att gora slut på sitt elandiga liv. Men innan han lamnar jordelivet vill han åka tillbaka till sin hemstad dar vagen mot undergången borjade. Ted har inget att forlora och tanker darfor ta en gruvlig hamnd på sin barndoms varsta plågoande, forodmjuka sin nu pensionerade mattelarare och ragga upp skolårens allra lackraste pudding. Men ingenting ar exakt som han forestallde sig. Och Teds sista stund på jorden kanske blir lite langre...

programme.title: Amores Perros
programme.desc: Karlek ar många saker — vissa bra, andra dåliga — men framfor allt suger den. En fruktansvard bilolycka binder samman tre berattelser, var och en med karaktarer som hanterar forlust, ånger och livets hårda verkligheter, allt i karlekens namn.

programme.desc: Travis (Terence Hills) ar vastens snabbaste revolverskytt. Hans bror Moses (Bud Spencer) ar stor som en bjorn och dubbelt så argsint og nybyggartrakternas mest hårdfora prisjagare. Når deras kara gamla mamma beslutar att återforena sina soner till jul blir det Travis uppgift att forsoka locka med sig Moses hem…

programme.title: Jul på bestallning
programme.desc: Gretchen får julen att handa var som helst och nar som helst.

programme.title: Julens Underland
programme.desc: Jultiden i NYC ar allt annat an underbar for den kampande artisten Heidi Neill.

programme.title: Catfish-julen
programme.desc: En hjartekrossad ung kvinna återvander hem over julen- och kanner pressen av att vara singel. Hennes karleksfulla och nyfikna syster planerar en natdejt- med en stilig idrottsman. Men det tar en ovantad vandning nar han inte ar hennes "prins i skinande rustning". Hennes barndomsvan visar henne att akta karlek kan finnas narmare hemmet.

programme.title: En perfekt jullista
programme.desc: Som en sista onskan ger en sjuk mormor sin dotter Michelle och barnbarnet Sara en lista over festliga prestationer att gora tillsammans fore jul, i hopp om att det ska reparera deras forhållande.

programme.title: A Taste Of Christmas
programme.desc: Nar Emily, en kampande bagare I en småstad, får en handgjord julkalender från en hemlig beundrare, blir lokalinvånarna besatta av att ta reda på avsandarens identitet. Julkalendern blir det stora skvallret i stan, och så blir aven Emilys amorosa aventyr, eftersom alla ungkarlar nu soker hennes uppmarksamhet. Men den man som fångar hennes intresse ar hennes varste konkurrent, den franske bagaren Gerard.

programme.title: A Christmas Movie Christmas
programme.desc: Systrarna Eve och Lacey onskar sig en jul precis som den i filmens varld. Innan de vet ordet av så upptacker de att dem ar fast i vad som faktiskt ar en julfilm. De vaknar upp i den sagolika staden ”Christmas Town”, den perfekta staden med den perfekta julen, dar allt bara ar perfekt. Ju mer de utforskar allt som har med hogtiden att gora inser de att perfektion kanske inte den ratta meningen for en traditionsenlig jul. Det kanske finns en annan magi med sonderbranda pepparkakor och overkokta julskinkor…?

programme.title: En Bennett-sång Holiday
programme.desc: Familjen Bennett-Song återvander till jul med stora nyheter. Mrs Song vantar ett barn som ska utoka listan på 14 adopterade barn! Familjen måste samarbeta for att ta sig an en maktig byggherre- som vill stanga farbrors kulturhus for handikappade och utsatta barn. Lite karlek, lagarbete och julmagi kommer att radda dagen.

programme.title: A Wedding for Christmas
programme.desc: Haley Foster flyttade från sin barndoms småstad Pineridge till storstadslivet i Los Angeles dar hon etablerat sig som hyllad brollopsplanerare på ett prestigefullt foretag som drivs av ms Reynolds.

programme.title: Christmas Land
programme.desc: Christmas Land har sett battre dagar sedan Glindas tragiska bortgång och Jules tvingas ta många komplicerade beslut.

programme.title: The Christmas Setup
programme.desc: Advokaten Hugo reser från New York till sin hemstad Milwaukie for att halsa på sin mamma. Mamman introducerar honom till sin gamla high school crush Patrick och det slår gnistor om paret. Hugo får dock sitt dromjobb som kraver en flytt till London och nu måste han valja – karriaren eller den nyfunna karleken.

programme.title: Julkupong
programme.desc: En fore detta skridskomastare borjar undervisa vid sin vans damm- och delar ut "kuponger" for att locka nya elever. Nar hennes fore detta ungdomskarlek (och nu kand hockeyspelare) tar med sin brorsdotter på lektioner, tands gamla flammor på nytt, och julen fylls med en andra chans for karlek.

programme.title: Ingen nåd sa Moses (The Troublemakers)
programme.desc: Travis (Terence Hills) ar vastens snabbaste revolverskytt. Hans bror Moses (Bud Spencer) ar stor som en bjorn och dubbelt så argsint og nybyggartrakternas mest hårdfora prisjagare. Når deras kara gamla mamma beslutar att återforena sina soner till jul blir det Travis uppgift att forsoka locka med sig Moses hem…

programme.title: High Holiday
programme.desc: Den frisinnade Liz ar inte så sugen på att ta med sin pojkvan hem till sin konservativa familj på julmiddag. Liz pojkvan foreslår att hon ska krydda salladsdressingen med marijuana for att latta upp stamningen. Kaos uppstår nar alla blir omedvetet hoga och avslojar familjens innersta hemligheter.

programme.title: The Loss Adjuster
programme.desc: En forsakringsman som kampar med forlust och karlek upptacker nya mojligheter under en vecka full av ovantade handelser och komiska vandpunkter.

programme.title: Silent Night: A Song for the World
programme.desc: Stilla natt, heliga natt - Joseph Mohrs heroiska resa 1818, nar han skapade varldens mest kanda julsång. Den sanna historien om låten berattas som en fiktiv historia.

programme.title: Forensic Files

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Forensic computer analysis, blood spatter analysis and a painstaking investigation lead police to a lawyer husband Michael "Mick" Fletcher with a motive to kill his wife since he was having a sexual affair with judge Susan Chrzanowski.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Susie Mowbray was charged for her husband Bill Mowbrays death, but her son was convinced of her innocence.

programme.title: Forensic Files

programme.title: Forensic Files

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: From 1985 to 1988, 18 people were choked, molested and left for dead in the remote mountains of California.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Nancy Newman and her two daughters are found brutally murdered. The crime scene has no shortage of evidence.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: In 1991, San Francisco pornographer Artie Mitchell was murdered in his home. His brother and business partner Jim is found near the scene carrying a rifle and later confesses to shooting Artie. The question is whether the shooting was premeditated.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: In 1989, 4-year-old April Loveless was found dead in the backyard of her Texas home. Her mother Debbie Loveless and stepfather John Miller told police that she was attacked and killed by the family dogs. Investigators did not agree.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: In 1992, Laura Houghteling disappeared from her Bethesda home and was never seen again. Lauras bedroom was searched and forensic science was used to direct them a to prime suspect.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: An investigation of a pediatrician, prompted by the death of one of her patients, leads to a Texas hospital where the pediatric mortality rate is higher than at any hospital in the country.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Eileen and Derrick Severs disappeared from their home in the small village of Hambleton in Great Britain.

programme.title: Forensic Files

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Eleven-month-old Chad Shelton was admitted to the hospital with unexplained bleeding and later died. Investigators and scientists frantically searched for a cause when others from the same house fell ill.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Police exhume the body of Karla Brown, murdered in her home in 1978, to study bite wounds, which eventually lead to the killer.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: On October 15, 1985, two bomb explosions rocked Salt Lake City and resulted in two deaths. A third explosion occurred the next day. This time, the victim was injured but survived.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A two-year-old boy was rushed to the hospital suffering from brain seizures and breathing difficulties.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Professional photographer Charles Rathbun claims model Linda Sobek died during a consensual sexual encounter gone wrong, but Sobeks corpse and some high-tech digital imagery tell a more sinister story.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Stephen Scher and Martin Dillon went skeet shooting on a beautiful spring day and Martin was shot dead.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: In 1995, police in San Diego, California are baffled by a pair of hands found in a dumpster. Through further investigation, they determine that the hands are those of missing person Don Hardin.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A woman disappeared and her husband became the prime suspect especially after police found a huge bloodstain on the carpet of their bedroom. Complex DNA testing proved it was the wifes blood. Now all they had to do was find her body.

programme.title: Forensic Files

programme.title: Forensic Files

programme.title: Forensic Files

programme.title: Buckskin Frontier

As political turmoil intensifies, the town becomes the center of a deadly conflict, where vengeance, power, and survival collide.

Guided by the chief’s son, Taslik, they face dwindling water and rising tensions. As suspicions grow, they notice Taslik wearing war paint. Is he leading them to peace or into a trap?

After rescuing a wagon under attack, Cisco discovers the victim was meant to replace Sanchez. Disguising himself as the victim, Cisco infiltrates Sanchezs operation to uncover evidence and bring justice to the rancho.

When the "Frenchman" is revealed to be Jeanne DuBois, she follows Cisco to his lair. As romance blooms, Cisco offers to return the silver to her. Along the way, he recruits a broken down, drunk prospector to help him track down the unknown tribe and rescue his sister.

programme.desc: 7 Days to Vegas is an edgy comedy that is based on a true story of the rise and fall of one of Hollywoods biggest poker games. The names have been changed to protect the guilty. Out of desperation to feed his family, Duke Hamilton, a washed up Hollywood actor in the 90s, starts up a small poker game from his house in the lower-class part of the San Fernando Valley. With the help of his wife KC, the game grows to attract some of the biggest players in the Los Angeles area. These risk-taking guys, who will bet on anything, live life on the edge. Its not just Poker that these spoiled LA moguls bet on.

programme.title: The Rules of Attraction - Lustans lagar
programme.desc: Jessica Biel, James Van Der Beek och Ian Somerhalder ger liv och skratt till den har arliga och skarpsinniga betraktelsen på sociala och sexuella forhållanden på college.

programme.title: The Hanged Man
programme.desc: After a condemned gunfighter (Steve Forrest) survives his own hanging, he helps a young widow stop a pitiless land baron from taking her ranch. This television feature boasts a strong cast of recognizable characters, including Will Geer, Sharon Acker, Dean Jagger, BarBara Luna, and Cameron Mitchell. Director Michael Caffey would go on to work on such hit shows as Barnaby Jones and MacGyver. Also, look for John Mitchum, younger brother of Robert, in a small role. This movie originally aired on ABC-TV and was considered the pilot for a possible series. Writer/producer Andrew Fenady was behind several opular TV shows such as Branded and The Rebel, as well as the 1970 John Wayne feature, Chisum.

programme.title: Man from Utah
programme.desc: WHIRLING ROPES AND SNARLING GUNS IN THE GALLOPING GRIP OF A GLAMOROUS DRAMA! John Wayne stars as John Weston, a man hired to investigate shady doings at a local rodeo. It seems all the riders who are on the verge of winning end up dead. Along with Wayne, this tale of action on the range also stars the usual Lone Star Picture stock company, including Gabby Hayes and Yakima Canutt!

programme.title: High Lonesome
programme.desc: A young drifter is suspected of murder in this stirring production from writer/director Alan Le May (best known for writing The Searchers). John Drew Barrymore stars as Cooncat, a troubled young man who has to steal to survive. With no friends in West Texas, he falls in with some bad customers who involve him in some terrible crimes. The strong cast includes Chill Wills, Jack Elam, and John Archer, with cinematography by Oscar winner W. Howard Greene.

programme.title: Courageous Avenger
programme.desc: Gold, gangs, and the heroic fight for life! Johnny Mack Brown (Billy the Kid, Coquette) stars in this western thriller about murders going on in a mining community. Its a story full of twists, where the greed for gold is only surpassed by the struggle for life!

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: A love story and a search for gold in the Valley of Death! Dubbed simple, powerful and dramatic by the New York Times on the date of its release, Death Valley is indeed an elegant depiction of love and deception in the American desert during the Gold Rush. In what was to be the final film of famed silent film director Paul Powell (Polyanna), a cast of mostly unknown actors produces uniformly excellent work. Lyrical and graceful, Powells film spins the tale of a young boy who finds love and gold, only to have it stolen from him.

programme.title: The Fighting Redhead

Saddle up and hang on!

Find out what happens in this fictional tale packed with action from 1951!

Unfortunately, the scoundrel Ralph Merritt (Sidney Blackmer) wants the cattle, and hes not above hiring some dangerous characters to do his dirty work. Its a test of blazing guns...under a blazing sun! Can the boys of Bar 20 lay down the law in a lawless place like the Pampas? Can Hoppy and his gang succeed in what is truly a last frontier? Watch and see!
